        "text": "62-83894\nRECORDED - 42\n62-83894-287\nDate: August 8, 1952\nEX-129\nTo:\nDirector of Special Investigations\nThe Inspector General\nDepartment of the Air Force\nThe Pentagon\nWashington 25, D. C.\nFrom:\nJohn Edgar Hoover - Director\nFederal Bureau of Investigation\nSubject:\nAERIAL OBJECTS;\n\"FLYING SAUCERS\"\nMISCELLANEOUS - INFORMATION CONCERNING\nThere are attached two copies of a letter dated"
      },
      "translation": {
        "text": "62-83894\n기록됨 - 42\n62-83894-287\n날짜: 1952년 8월 8일\nEX-129\n수신:\n특별 수사 국장\n감찰관\n공군부\n펜타곤\n워싱턴 25, D. C.\n발신:\n존 에드거 후버 - 국장\n연방 수사국\n제목:\n공중 물체;\n\"비행접시\"\n기타 - 관련 정보\n첨부된 서신 두 부는 날짜가",
